com.avaya.ic.sdk
Interface ICPropertyStore

public interface ICPropertyStore

Represents a store for all IC properties that are sent from the server to the client. You can configure the property sections to be sent to the client in the SDKICPropertiesSections.properties file. The values of the ICProperties sent from the server are specific to the user. For more information about the SDKICPropertiesSections.properties file, see the Client SDK Programmer Guide.
